   <concept id="FAR_52_232_15" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">52.232-15</ph> Progress Payments Not Included.</title>
      <conbody outputclass="clause" class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p class="- topic/p " id="d3513e8">As prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="32.502-3.dita#FAR_32_502_3"
                     base="i1082131"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">32.502-3</xref>(c)</ph>, insert the following provision in invitations for bids if the solicitation will not contain one of the provisions prescribed in <ph outputclass="ClauseProvisionXREF" class="- topic/ph ">
               <xref href="32.502-3.dita#FAR_32_502_3"
                     base="i1082131"
                     outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                     class="- topic/xref ">32.502-3</xref>
            </ph>(a) and (b):</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Ctr_SmCaps" id="d3513e19">Progress Payments Not Included <ph outputclass="SmCaps" class="- topic/ph ">(Apr 1984)</ph>
         </p>
         <p class="- topic/p ">A progress payments clause is not included in this solicitation, and will not be added to the resulting contract at the time of award. Bids conditioned upon inclusion of a progress payment clause in the resulting contract will be rejected as nonresponsive.</p>
         <p class="- topic/p " outputclass="Endofclause">(End of clause)</p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
